                            <comment id="12631991" author="phunt" created="Thu, 18 Sep 2008 00:00:26 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch adds a new WatcherTest to verify the failure condition. I&apos;ve updated the clientcnxn code (and zookeeper.java) to correctly materialize the watchers that need to process an incoming watch event.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All tests now pass, including the new test case that explicitly verifies this case.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note: hudson has been seeing intermittent failures due to this issue. ClientTest was occasionally failing due to missing events.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
